title: Open Bar #88 - The Acolyte, George Lucas Sells Out, Alien Romulus Trailer
description:
It's trailer-tastic this week as we've just had trailers for The Acolyte, House of the Dragon Season 2 and Alien: Romulus. Plus, bad news for the 20 or so Star Wars fans that are left, as George Lucas puts his weight behind Bob Iger in the proxy battle for the Disney board. Join me, MauLer, Ryan Kinel, Robot Head and The Angry Badger as we talk about all of it. 

Subscribe to Ryan Kinel: https://www.youtube.com/@ryankinel-rkoutpost1
Subscribe to Robot Head: https://www.youtube.com/@RobotHead
Subscribe to The Angry Badger: https://www.youtube.com/@TheAngryBadger3

title: The Acolyte - The Message Is Strong With This One
description: Another day, another crushingly mediocre Star Wars product from Disney Lucasfilm to consume. Let's get this over and take a look at the first trailer for The Acolyte.
